body:
Good Morning Riot Bug Team,

I recently bought the Master Yi Chroma pack a couple of days ago. After completing my purchase I received 3 consecutive error windows (for each color skin within the chroma pack I assume) and have been unable to use the chroma&#039;s in game. I have restarted the client multiple times, and have tried methods such as re-selecting or re-creating my teambuilder session. However, everytime I get in game my selected chroma&#039;s are not loading. I am unsure if this is strictly a client issue or if it&#039;s an account issue.

Please help! {{champion:11}}
